                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/37e63f92-9f0d-11e4-91b3-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/37e63f92-9f0d-11e4-91b3-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Inode 170393601 ref count is 1, should be 40.  Fix? no
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Though this failure happened in test_17n, but it is actually caused by some test between 17n and 65, i.e. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;run MDSCOUNT=4 ONLY=18-66 sh sanity.sh&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;then do e2fsck -fnvd mdt2 should reproduce the ticket. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
